2. pipe
you can use Pipes (|) to stream STDOUT from previous command as STDIN of subsequent
cat states.txt | wc -l

3. getting help
if you need help for a specific command, use man [command]

4. Tools for batch scripting
vim
• i switch to insert mode
• Esc back to command mode
• Navigation: h j k l, by word W w
• :wq save and exit
